fields.fieldDescription: Indicates the type of lender:  Primary (PRI)  Primary Assignment (PASG)  Undecided (null)
The unique id of the lender in Loan IQ with which is represented by this row.

'Y' indicates that this lender is a primary which is a fronting bank in the syndication process.
'Y' indicates that this lender is a primary which is the lead fronting bank in the syndication process.
